    - "WasteBin_Teacher" near teacher desk left side.

    - Arrange in two rows of three, evenly spaced along ceiling.

    - Place 3 on left wall, 3 on right wall, 2 on back wall: total 8.
    - Names: "Poster_{wall}_{i}".
    - Size each: 0.6m x 0.4m x 0.02m.
    - Mounted at 1.5m height, evenly spaced horizontally.

    - Teacher desk and chair: dark wood tones.
    - Walls: soft neutral white paint.
    - Floor: light-colored wood or tile.
